{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_09_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 我慢するのはもったいない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Moon Tempest became BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 2.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日もお疲れ様。生放送にインタビュー、CM撮影\nまであって大忙しだったな。体調は大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work today. Live broadcast‚ interview‚ and CM shooting…\nIt's been a really busy day. Are you feeling okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。むしろ{user}さんこそ\n疲れた顔されてませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine. Rather‚ {user}-san‚ you're the one\nwho looks tired‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "う、鋭いな。今度の打ち合わせ用に資料を作っていたら\nつい熱が入って……気付けば日付が変わっていてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ you're sharp. I was making materials for the next meeting‚\nand I got so into it… It was already the next day before I knew it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私達のために、遅くまでありがとうございます\nでも、たまには自分の体も労わって下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for staying up so late for us.\nBut‚ please take care of your own body sometimes too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。もうすぐ新曲のMV撮影もあるし\nお互い体調には気をつけていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. We have an MV shoot for a new song soon‚\nso let's be careful about our health.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だが、これだけ過密なスケジュールなのに\n沙季は普段とまるで変わらないな。本当に凄いよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even with such a tight schedule‚\nYou’re just like always. You're really amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私の場合、千紗の忙しさをそばで見ていたのが\n大きいですね。その分、覚悟は出来ていましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In my case‚ seeing how busy Chisa was\nup close was a big help. Because of that‚ I was prepared for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、睡眠や食事は必ず十分に取ること\nそれ以外のことも表にまとめて、焦らず行動すること",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ I make sure to get enough sleep and eat properly.\nI also organize things into tables‚ and act without rushing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが組んだスケジュールに\n無理はないはずですし、一つ一つこなせば大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The schedule that {user}-san put together\nisn't too demanding‚ and it'll be okay if I take care of each task one by one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8944863583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "もし体調を崩してしまう子がいたら、出来る限り\nフォローしますから、いつでも頼って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If someone’s feeling unwell‚ I'll do my best\nto support her‚ so please rely on me anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗を間近で見ていたからこそ、ってことか\n沙季みたいに冷静な子がいると、周りも安心出来そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it's because you were watching Chisa up close.\nHaving someone as calm as Saki around is reassuring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ。アイドルとしてお仕事を沢山いただけるのは\n嬉しいですし、みんなで乗り切っていきたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no. I'm happy to have so much work as an idol‚\nand I want to get through it with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1227160057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、忙しいのはありがたいんですが……最近はお断り\nしている仕事が増えてしまってるのが心苦しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ while I'm grateful for being busy… Recently‚\nI've had to turn down more and more offers‚ and it pains me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季の時間や体力にも限界があるからな。なるべく多く\n受けられるよう調整しているんだが、申し訳ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a limit to Saki's time and energy. I'm trying to adjust\nthe schedule so that you can take on as much as possible‚ but I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2204013955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ希望は尊重したいと思ってるから、優先したい\n仕事や、やってみたい仕事があったら教えてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I want to respect your wishes‚ so if there's any work\nyou want to prioritize or try‚ please tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "優先したい仕事……そうですね、そういう意味では\nレギュラー出演している番組を、何より優先したいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Work I want to prioritize… Well‚ in that sense‚\nI want to prioritize the programs I'm a regular on above all else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "これまでいただいたお仕事があったからこそ\n今の私がありますから。しっかりとご恩に報いたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The work I've had until now has made me\nwho I am today. I want to repay the kindness I've received.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、新しいお仕事の話も聞いてみたいですね\n指名してもらうからには、出来る限り頑張りたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'd like to hear about new jobs too.\nSince I'm getting nominated‚ I want to do my best as much as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "その上で、希望があるとすれば……自分の趣味を\n生かせるようなお仕事に挑戦してみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On top of that‚ if I could make a request…… I'd like to\ntry my hand at a job that lets me use my hobbies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "実は、千紗がホラーやファッション関係のお仕事を\nしてるのがちょっとだけ羨ましくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I'm a little envious of Chisa\nfor doing work related to horror or fashion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら、今より多少忙しくなっても頑張ります\nまだ体力には余裕もありますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's for that‚ I'll do my best even if I get a little busier than now.\nI still have plenty of stamina.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな\nよし、それじゃあ今度の打ち合わせで話してみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nAlright‚ I'll talk about it at the next meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.1666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.1166713317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.1166713317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.2333335876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、始まりました！\n『街中探検・ぐるっとスタンプラリー』のお時間です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ it's starting!\nIt's time for \"City Exploration - Round and Round Stamp Rally\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.2333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.1000046651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "今日は私、白石沙季と一緒に、スタンプラリーを\n通してこの街のことをより深く知っていきましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I‚ Shiraishi Saki‚ will be exploring\nthis city with you through the stamp rally!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（さすがに自分から提案した企画だけに）\n（凄い熱の入りようだ）\n（局との打ち合わせに）\n（企画書持参で逆提案したんだもんな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（As expected‚ since it's a project she proposed herself‚）\n（She's putting so much enthusiasm into it.）\n（At the meeting with the station‚）\n（she brought a proposal and made a suggestion.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.9666713317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、ここが一つ目のスタンプを押せる場所ですね\n現地の方にこの土地ゆかりのお話をうかがいましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ this is the first place you can get a stamp.\nLet's ask the locals about the history of this land.",
