      "text": "戦場だけでなく、領内の治水事業でも腕を振るった文武\n両道な方ですよね。本を読んでいて胸が躍りました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He was skilled in both warfare and literature‚ using his skills not only on the battlefield but also\nin flood control projects within his territory. I was thrilled when I read about him in a book!",
